WEBVTT

00:00.036 --> 00:01.835
<i>Previously on The Borgias...</i>

00:01.937 --> 00:04.105
Giovanni Sforza.

00:04.173 --> 00:06.341
And my cousin,
Catherina Sforza.

00:06.402 --> 00:08.424
You would have a
taste of vengeance.

00:08.492 --> 00:09.995
<i>The king</i>
<i>is on the move.</i>

00:10.063 --> 00:11.330
He says he will
use his cannon

00:11.393 --> 00:13.359
to reduce our
walls to dust.

00:13.428 --> 00:15.860
We fight fire with fire.

00:15.928 --> 00:17.494
You tricked the French King

00:17.562 --> 00:19.461
and now he comes
for our blood!

00:19.528 --> 00:22.129
Do you expect us to
support you twice?

00:23.535 --> 00:24.972
Do you know what this is?

00:25.040 --> 00:27.348
It is the fresco you have so
graciously commissioned.

00:27.415 --> 00:28.715
But it lacks a model.

00:28.783 --> 00:30.184
I would restore this hair

00:30.251 --> 00:32.891
to what it was
before God snatched it from me.

00:32.959 --> 00:34.760
Will we meet again,
Holy Father?

00:34.828 --> 00:36.565
Perhaps.
Am I to be your mistress then?

00:36.666 --> 00:37.633
No.

00:37.734 --> 00:39.101
That position is taken.

00:39.169 --> 00:41.005
We will have you go
through your accounts

00:41.072 --> 00:43.344
with one we have designated
to supervise them.

00:43.413 --> 00:44.981
Unthinkable!

00:45.048 --> 00:46.950
That monies destined to the
poor should go to the poor?

00:47.017 --> 00:50.156
That a woman have access
to curatorial accounts.

00:50.224 --> 00:52.360
<i>The French are</i>
<i>advancing from Naples.</i>

00:52.429 --> 00:55.766
They may murder th
Borgia pe for you.

00:55.834 --> 00:57.367
<i>We would discuss</i>
<i>another cousin</i>

00:57.435 --> 01:00.773
in whose hands the survival
of our papacy may lie.

01:00.841 --> 01:03.310
<i>Your Holiness refers</i>
<i>to the Duke of Milan.</i>

01:03.377 --> 01:05.144
This is true artistry.

01:05.212 --> 01:06.881
Indeed, my lord.
It is but plaster.

01:06.948 --> 01:09.183
There are-
Ninety-five more like it-

01:09.251 --> 01:11.954
making their way from other
foundries as we speak.

01:12.022 --> 01:14.023
You are denied entry
to Rome, my liege.

01:14.091 --> 01:15.793
My cannon will gain me entry.

01:15.861 --> 01:19.030
Perhaps my cannon will make
their statement first.

01:19.098 --> 01:20.331
I warn you!

01:20.399 --> 01:22.033
I shall take terrible revenge!

01:22.134 --> 01:24.135
On you, your family,

01:24.236 --> 01:25.970
and the papacy itself!

01:26.038 --> 01:27.605
Retreat!

01:30.108 --> 01:36.499
[♪]

01:36.599 --> 01:40.599
